company_name: SOCIEDAD DE EXPORTACION DE AGRIOS N 2 DE MONCOFAR COOP VALENCIA
information: The company SOCIEDAD DE EXPORTACION DE AGRIOS N 2 DE MONCOFAR COOP VALENCIA, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, which operates in the Fruit industry. It also operates in the Citrus fruits industries. It is based in Moncofa, Spain.
